{"type":"question","id":13696,"title":"哪些台湾媒体值得看？","uid":21532,"topics":[16],"contents":"我不喜欢呆在同温层，想要拼凑事实。在香港选择媒体我是参照<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/article/20191128/s00012/1574878673471/%E8%98%87%E9%91%B0%E6%A9%9F-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E5%85%AC%E4%BF%A1%E5%8A%9B-%E4%BD%8E%E8%99%95%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中文大学的传媒公信力调查</a>，确定每个媒体的立场。谷歌搜索<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93+%E5%85%AC%E4%BF%A1%E5%8A%9B\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">台湾媒体 公信力</a>只找到了<a href=\"http://www.mediawatch.org.tw/work/study\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">台灣媒體觀察教育基金會</a>2015年的<a href=\"http://www.mediawatch.org.tw/sites/default/files/files/0331%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%A1%E5%BA%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">一份报告</a>：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/oT1wvZb.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oT1wvZb.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/oT1wvZb.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/tUuUAzy.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tUuUAzy.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/tUuUAzy.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n这份报告已经是5年前了，相信情况已经有了很大变化。那么在五年后的今天，有哪些台湾媒体值得一看呢？<br>\n<br>\nBonus: <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/267039751\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">知乎奇文共赏 https://www.zhihu.com/question/267039751</a>","date":"2019-12-20","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":10}